5
00:00:17,420 --> 00:00:21,350
You should check if your application can do without microservices.

6
00:00:21,890 --> 00:00:28,370
When your application requires a high level of independent scalability and requires agility to time

7
00:00:28,370 --> 00:00:34,880
to market with zero downtime deployments and updated independently, that needs to more flexibility,

8
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:38,000
