Developers tend to focus too much on the latest technology tools, for example, microservices.

11
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:59,120
Instead of that, developers and architects should consider the reasons why for implementation, and

12
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:05,030
they should also focus on the result that the technology tools drive to achieve that results.

13
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:12,410
Another reason is iterate with small changes and keep the single process monolithic as your default.

14
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:19,370
When we talk about modular monolithic architecture, we saw that Sam Nunn and Martin Fowler offers monolithic

15
00:01:19,370 --> 00:01:26,750
first approaches, because modular architecture also covers a lot of benefits of microservices, with

16
