23
00:01:58,170 --> 00:01:59,430
After all these things.

24
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:05,970
If your application required to independently deploy new functionality with zero downtime, then microservices

25
00:02:05,970 --> 00:02:07,380
are extremely useful.

26
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:14,160
When organization need to make a change to functionality and deploy that functionality without affecting

27
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,270
